{"tid":967452,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"［抉擇］條女唔愛我？","createTime":"2019-01-03T13:25:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-04T04:12:30.000Z","uid":143079,"like":102,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"5248fea3a74ccae37a377e3d184368932e662615","tid":967452,"uid":143079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T13:25:21.000Z","msg":"拍咗半年拖 一直都好sweet<br />\n我成日比surprise佢 佢話想要咩<br />\n我會偷偷地買 過幾日送比佢<br />\n佢每次都好開心 話我好傻 係咪on9嫁真係買比我<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n見到佢個開心樣我就覺得一切都好值得<br />\n<br />\n到咗最近 佢開始返工好忙 又話有好多野要做<br />\n冇乜時間見面 咁就大家番工去到24號先見<br />\n我一早就買咗份佢想買好耐既禮物比佢<br />\n到咗24號一出黎 我就比咗份禮物佢<br />\n佢個樣係好驚訝 然後就低頭好似有野諗咁<br />\n之後講咗句多謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁佢嗰日就咁帶個戒波袋就出黎<br />\n應該冇禮物比我了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔緊要啦 佢應該係聽日正日先送<br />\n結果到咗今日 佢仍然係手fingfing<br />\n我唔係貪d乜野 我只係好想知道佢對我仲有冇愛<br />\n唉 我唔知道 我有chok下佢 但佢只係話好忙冇時間<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好撚明顯佢就係當你兵 咪撚傻啦分手啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢都話忙啫 唔洗咁緊張喎"},{"pid":"f514c522e2a219eefe4a819e02db4f6529a7c91d","tid":967452,"uid":140234,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T13:31:16.000Z","msg":"唔係阿 佢幾愛你d禮物阿<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a706eebdf08959ad20ff31b3694f5c3b575462d0","tid":967452,"uid":212623,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T13:33:24.000Z","msg":"大水魚 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f5a67dcd298cf37fc2948430090041aa5157453","tid":967452,"uid":113007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T13:33:31.000Z","msg":"你想要乜野禮物？"},{"pid":"9da69132dae262c99e832c90a99a89e392d637f7","tid":967452,"uid":104138,"like":29,"dislike":1,"score":28